      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     stp-srt-inp-141
                     stp-srt-inp-142
                     stp-srt-inp-143
                     depending            on   rr-sts-cdp             .
       stp-srt-inp-141.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se solo commesse da evadere             *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Test su flag di commessa comunque   *
      *                          * saldata                             *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        rf-cdp-sdc-ccs       not  = spaces
