      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     let-arc-ycp-999.
       let-arc-ycp-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Azioni per record non trovato                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "#"                  to   w-let-arc-ycp-flg      .
           move      all   "."            to   w-let-arc-ycp-des      .
           go to     let-arc-ycp-600.
       let-arc-ycp-500.
